@baseUrl = http://localhost:8096

###
### Error Handling Tests
### Tests various error scenarios: 404, 405, 400, 415, validation errors, etc.
### All errors return structured JSON ErrorResponse: { "status", "error", "message", "path", "fieldErrors" (optional) }
### Key fields for quick checks: "error" and "message" (set by GlobalRestExceptionHandler)
###

### Test 404 - Non-existent endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nonexistent
Accept: application/json

### Test 405 - Method not allowed (POST to GET endpoint)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uuid
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 400 - Bad Request (Invalid JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invalid": "json",
  "missing": "closing brace"

### Test 400 - Missing required parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten
Accept: text/plain

### Test 400 - Blank required parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=
Accept: text/plain

### Test 415 - Unsupported Media Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paste
Content-Type: text/plain

content=test

### Test validation error - Invalid paste content (empty content)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paste
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": ""
}

### Test large payload - Very long content
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paste
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. This content is repeated many times to simulate a large payload..."
}

### Test special characters in URL parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=https://example.com/test?param=<script>alert('xss')</script>
Accept: text/plain

### Test SQL injection attempt in paste content
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paste
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "'; DROP TABLE pastes; --"
}